Science Documentary hosted by Morgan Freeman, published by Discovery Channel in 2016 - English narration 
http://docuwiki.net/images/3/3c/Through-the-Wormhole-Series-7-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------

Through the Wormhole: Series 7
Hosted by Morgan Freeman, Through the Wormhole will explore the deepest mysteries of existence - the questions that have puzzled mankind for eternity. What are we made of? What was there before the beginning? 


4)  Can We All Become Geniuses 
Genius lies somewhere in the human mind, bringing mathematical insight, sparking artistic inspiration and enabling some to see what most cannot. Might we augment our biology with technology to unlock the genius inside us all?
